title: Quake 1 Original Full With Darkplaces Engine (Working Music)
description:
This is the original Quake running with the Darkplaces Sourceport. There is no mods, no map edits, etc. Just run the exe to extract and its ready to play. Music will work in this also. The Darkplaces Engine is a 2008 version as it works best with xp. If you feel the need to update it, you can pick up newer versions here: http://icculus.org/twilight/darkplaces/

Just download the desired engine version and extract into the quake folder. (do not put in Id1 folder)
